high_descs: Turn to the right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is closest to the sink basin.
Turn to the right and walk to the stove.
Place the knife into the pan on the stove.
Pick the pan up from the stove burner.
Turn left and walk over the the counter with the coffeemaker.
Place the pan on the counter in front of the coffeemaker.
anns.task_desc: Placing a pan containing a knife onto the counter from the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight towards the oven, turn right at the sink, go to the sink.
Take the large knife that is more to the left from in front of the sink.
Turn right, go straight, before reaching the wall turn right, go straight until the oven is to the left, face the oven.
Put the knife in the pot on the right of the stove top.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go straight, turn left when the white table is to the left.
Put the pot to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the leftmost knife on counter in front of the sink.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the knife.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the pot with the knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on the table.
